<page title="ldapvi" style="ldapvi.css">
  <intro>
    <p>
      <tt>ldapvi</tt> is an interactive LDAP client for Unix terminals.
      Using it, you can update LDAP entries with a text editor.<br/>
      Think of it as <tt>vipw</tt>(1) for LDAP.
    </p>
    <p>
      ldapvi was written by David Lichteblau.
    </p>
  </intro>

  <section title="Documentation">
